      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? You've found it! I've taken absolute pride in keeping this beauty in flawless condition. It\u2019s been babied since day one\u2014always garaged, regularly detailed, and runs like an absolute dream. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection. I'm honestly a bit sad to see it go, but I know it'll make its next owner super happy. Come take a look and see for yourself!",
