      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an exceptional 2002 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This collector-grade example boasts a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and remains in peak mechanical form. The individual throttle bodies have been meticulously synced, and the engine benefits from proactive rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul. The chassis is structurally flawless, featuring a reinforced rear subframe to ensure long-term torsional rigidity. Every aspect of the suspension geometry remains true, with the Variable M Differential Lock providing precise power delivery. Finished in a deep luster with a pristine Nappa leather interior, this vehicle represents a turnkey opportunity for the discerning purist seeking a masterpiece of Bavarian engineering.",
